publisher			TBA Games							
publish_time	 2015年2月19日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							PeriAreion, a term meaning "closest approach to Mars", is a single-player realistic space sim/strategy game. The goal is to establish a sustainable colony on Mars by mining minerals, constructing and populating a base, and dealing with the hazards of such a harsh environment. Like Oregon Trail in space, PeriAreion is about exploring a new and unforgiving frontier. All the science, modules, and environments found in the game are based upon current mars research and mission concepts.Key Features:CONSTRUCT YOUR BASEBuild and upgrade a variety of modules to help your colonists survive. Each module provides a unique and vital function to your base as well as enabling research in one of the 4 module tech trees.EXPLORE MARSPlay on 3 unique maps all generated from sattellite imagery of Mars. Each map has different weather and hazards, along with difficulties for navigation and resource location. Find points of interest, missions, minerals, ice, and photo oppotunities as you explore.RESEARCH COLONY UPGRADESSpend research points in 5 different trees with 71 possible upgrades. This includes 3 different colony specializations that determine your path to sustainability and change the way you win the game.LEARN ABOUT MARSUnlock articles in the PeriAreipedia containing the latest research and science about Mars. Get new articles for completing missions, constructing modules, and performing research.						
title	 PeriAreion			
